 them on for example.  What if they found out they carried a deadly genetic disorder and could not face watching their baby die painfully before they were 5 or carry the burden of a 60 year old incompetent with a mental age of 3 for their entire life?  What if they faced a personal choice and didn't feel like clearing it with you for permission or justifying a very difficult and horrible decision with the supreme court and all the tabloids?<br>
